metadata.name: The Tapping of Tai Lam Chung, 2021
metadata.description:
This 2021 work features seigaiha patterning and depicts a vista from Hong Kong's Tai Lam Country Park. Disembodied hands pay a tribute of thanks using familiar local gestures.

Original Artwork Information

Media: Acrylic on wood panel
Dimensions: 24 x 18 x 7/8 inches (60.9 x 45.7 x 2.2 cm), with painted wraparound
Availability: No; original work not for sale and not included with purchase of NFT
